 * | Ctrl |      | PGDN | Win  |||||||| Alt  | Space| Lower|||||||| Raise| Enter| RAlt ||||||||      | PGUP | Ins  | RCtrl|
 * .----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------.
 */
                        bindings = < 
&kp  ESC      &kp  Q        &kp  W        &kp  E        &kp  R        &kp  T        &none            &none      &kp  Y        &kp  U        &kp  I        &kp  O        &kp  P        &kp  BSPC       
&kp  TAB      &kp  A        &kp  S        &kp  D        &lt 3 F        &kp  G        &none            &none      &kp  H        &kp  J        &kp  K        &kp  L        &kp  SEMI     &kp  SQT       
&kp  LSHFT    &kp  Z        &kp  X        &kp  C        &kp  V        &lt 5 B        &none            &none      &kp  N        &kp  M        &kp  COMMA    &kp  DOT      &kp  SLASH    &kp  BSLH      
